OL,3,CRising demand at Belfast food kitchen
OL,5,FA food kitchen in north Belfast says
OL,6,Fdemand has increased year-on-year as
OL,7,FBelfast grapples with continuing
OL,8,Fpoverty and homelessness on the city's
OL,9,Fstreets.
OL,11,FThe People's Kitchen at Carlisle
OL,12,FCircus is serving up hot breakfasts to
OL,13,Fthose most in need including on
OL,14,FChristmas Day.
OL,16,FThose who run it say last weekend saw
OL,17,Fa huge response.
