OL,3,CRising demand at Belfast food kitchen
OL,5,F"Numbers have doubled and continue to
OL,6,Fincrease," said Paul McCusker. "I mean
OL,7,Fwe provide a breakfast Monday to
OL,8,FThursday from 8:30 to 11, we do
OL,9,Foutreach 7 nights a week and also we
OL,10,Fdo a drop-in at weekends.
OL,12,F"Last weekend we had over 100 people
OL,13,Fpresent just for a sit-in meal but
OL,14,Falso people then present for takeaways
OL,15,Ftoo, so we've certainly seen a massive
OL,16,Fincrease in people who are struggling."
