OL,3,CRising demand at Belfast food kitchen
OL,5,F"So these people are quite, you know,
OL,6,Fthey're struggling and they're
OL,7,Freaching out for support, and the main
OL,8,Fthing for us at The People's Kitchen
OL,9,Fis to try and advocate and try and get
OL,10,Fpeople off the streets for Christmas.
OL,12,F"The situation on the streets sadly
OL,13,Fhas deteriorated and has been for a
OL,14,Fnumber of years.
OL,16,F"We're seeing more people who are in
OL,17,Ftents, people who are under bridges,
OL,18,Fpeople who are who are sleeping rough,
OL,19,Fso it's a big concern, has been a big
OL,20,Fconcern for us for quite some time."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
