OL,3,CRising demand at Belfast food kitchen
OL,5,FWhether it's for a Christmas brekkie,
OL,6,Fbanter, or to bond over a chat, this
OL,7,Fservice on a busy street corner is
OL,8,Faiming to keep people safe, warm and
OL,9,Ffed.
OL,11,F"The response in terms of donations
OL,12,Fhas been incredible," Paul McCusker
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,F"I mean, people sending cheques in the
OL,16,Fpost to people coming down with
OL,17,Fclothes, sleeping bags, food, and
OL,18,Fyesterday we got a nice call from Gary
OL,19,FLightbody from Snow Patrol who's
OL,20,Fdonated #20,000 to the project as well.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/6
